course_description: Pre-Requisites: BIOS 503D and PRS 535D as prerequisites or special permission required to enroll. Provides students with an introduction to measurement methods and basic knowledge of quantitative applications using SAS Enterprise software. Content will stress specific skills and knowledge of working with data sets using basic SAS functions to analyze research questions and hypotheses, perform appropriate data analysis procedures, and interpret data outputs.
